<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
    <title>Examples</title>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="http://sf.pandawork.net/resources/js/app/site-config.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="http://sf.pandawork.net/resources/js/base/lib/kissy/seed.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>
        Defender新增功能： 通过给input添加data-valid-pattern="[reg]"属性，设置正则匹配，可以极大地节省正则验证的开发时间。
    </h2>
    <p>如下例：isbn需要是7为数字(或者'X')或者13为数字(或者'X')</p>
    <form action="path/1" id="J_form">
        <p>
            <label for="isbn">ISBN:</label>
            <input type="text" id="isbn" data-valid-pattern="^[\d|x|X]{7}$|^[\d|x|X]{13}$" data-valid-tip="输入isbn|isbn不符合规则">
        </p>
        <p>
            <button type="submit">submit</button>
        </p>
    </form>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        KISSY.use('mod/defender', function(){
            PW.mod.Defender('#J_form', {
                theme: 'inline'
            })
        })
    </script>
</body>
</html>